\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104jxv1665702990013.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jxv1665702990013.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jxv1665702990013.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"jxv1665702990013\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The [background] and [foreground] sections of <span class=\"ph filepath\">psddef.txt</span> determine how PostScript color definitions are mapped to PostScript colors.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"jxv1665702990013__topic_d176471e1_d176472e1_d176473e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jxv1665702990013__p_d176474e1_d176475e1_d176476e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">[background]</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">LogicalColorName</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">:</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ColorDefinition</var> {<var class=\"keyword varname\">Color</var>}</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jxv1665702990013__p_d176477e1_d176478e1_d176479e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">[foreground]</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">LogicalColorName</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">:</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ColorDefinition</var> {<var class=\"keyword varname\">Color</var>}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section table\" id=\"jxv1665702990013__section_w5612ab1b5b3_w5613ab1b5_w5614ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"jxv1665702990013__table_d18593e1_d18594e1_d18595e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Configuration file:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"ph filepath\">psdfef.txt</span> (Unix\n                        only)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Arguments</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Description</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">ColorName</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Logical color name</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">ColorDefinition</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Color definition, expressed as a percentage of\n                        Red Green Blue color definitions. For example, <code class=\"ph codeph\">1.00 0.00\n                           0.00</code> is equivalent to <code class=\"ph codeph\">255,0,0</code>, and <code class=\"ph codeph\">0.5\n                           0.00 0.00</code> is equivalent to <code class=\"ph codeph\">127,0,0</code>.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Color</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Optional name of the color. It is treated as a\n                        comment and is used only to describe the color for users.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jxv1665702990013__section_prm_lj1_dcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d543916e173\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">If you have changed the color definitions in the [background] and [foreground] sections\n            of <span class=\"ph filepath\">usys.ini</span>, you should change the definitions in this section.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"jxv1665702990013__pre_mjz_clm_gxb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[background]\ncolor_0: 0.75 0.75 0.75 grey\ncolor_1: 0.00 0.00 1.00 blue\ncolor_2: 0.00 1.00 0.00 green\ncolor_3: 0.00 1.00 1.00 cyan\ncolor_4: 1.00 0.00 0.00 red\ncolor_5: 1.00 0.00 1.00 magenta\ncolor_6: 1.00 1.00 0.00 yellow\ncolor_7: 1.00 1.00 1.00 white\n...</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529097\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529097\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "[background] and [foreground] Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 The [background] and [foreground] sections of psddef.txt determine how PostScript color definitions are mapped to PostScript colors. [background] LogicalColorName : ColorDefinition { Color } [foreground] LogicalColorName : ColorDefinition { Color } Configuration file: psdfef.txt (Unix only) Arguments Description ColorName Logical color name ColorDefinition Color definition, expressed as a percentage of Red Green Blue color definitions. For example, 1.00 0.00 0.00 is equivalent to 255,0,0 , and 0.5 0.00 0.00 is equivalent to 127,0,0 . Color Optional name of the color. It is treated as a comment and is used only to describe the color for users. Description If you have changed the color definitions in the [background] and [foreground] sections of usys.ini , you should change the definitions in this section. For example: [background] color_0: 0.75 0.75 0.75 grey color_1: 0.00 0.00 1.00 blue color_2: 0.00 1.00 0.00 green color_3: 0.00 1.00 1.00 cyan color_4: 1.00 0.00 0.00 red color_5: 1.00 0.00 1.00 magenta color_6: 1.00 1.00 0.00 yellow color_7: 1.00 1.00 1.00 white ... Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}